    <abstract>
      <t>This draft describes a new TLS extension for in-band transport of the complete set of DNSSEC validated records needed to perform DANE authentication of a TLS server without the need to perform separate out-of-band DNS lookups. When the requisite DNS records do not exist, the extension conveys a validated denial of existence proof.</t>
